    "Condition : 1 - Schedule\r\nThe addition of the wrapped column on the ground floor; \r\nThe amendment to the extent of the green material above this column\r\nThe addition of a balustrade behind the opening to the 8th floor plant room. ",
    "Reason : 1 - Within the context of planning application P/1656/20 granted on 27/04/2021, the proposed addition of columns within the ground floor car parking/servicing area could result in a material change to the accessibility of the ground floor accessible car parking and servicing area. It would therefore require re-consultation of the Local Highways Authority and the proposal would need to be re-assessed to ensure suitable accessible car parking would be provided within the curtilage of the site, in accordance with the requirements of policy T6 of The London Plan (2021) and policies DM1, DM42 and DM44 of the Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013). The proposal is therefore not considered to be non-material minor amendment."
